{
  "stem": "24259.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And every time our families would get together, certain things would be brought up, and discussed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was, obviously, confiscated by the Germans when they came in, and then eventually just became part of the Russian property when the Russians liberated us and we left the area.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, briefly my parents and I returned to the farm after the war when we were liberated by the Russians, but we were just there for a very short period of time.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the ghetto was a combined Jewish population of Mlynov and Muravic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was in-- in that general area.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were just a few thousand Jewish inhabitants from both towns.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were very few people there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto was just my father, my mother, and I.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there were other-- obviously, other members of my mother's family and my father's family were also in the ghetto as well.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother and my father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in the ghetto approximately about a year.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember anything specifically.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I am told of an incident where my parents have told me that when the word got out that the Germans came in, I-- I hid-- hid out, and they were looking for me everywhere, and I had hidden myself somewhere.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the house.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I guess it was just a fear or whatever, and I suppose listening to what was going on, and so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I personally don't remember any specifics during that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when the Germans came into our area, I'm told, of course, they rounded up the Jews and marched them to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They also forced some of them to do certain labor.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
